OL,6,FA woman has been charged in court with
OL,7,Fthe murder of a 90-year-old former
OL,8,Fphysicist.
OL,10,FMyra Thompson was found dead by
OL,11,Fambulance crews in her home in Spital,
OL,12,FWirral, on 23 April.
OL,14,FJane Hill, 51, was charged with murder
OL,15,Fand the theft of #60, alleged to have
OL,16,Fbeen taken from Ms Thompson on 12
OL,17,FApril.
