OL,6,FHill, of Norwich Drive in Upton,
OL,7,FWirral, spoke through tears while
OL,8,Fclutching tissues to confirm her name,
OL,9,Fdate of birth and address at Liverpool
OL,10,FMagistrates' Court. She was wearing a
OL,11,Fgrey jumper with her hair tied back.
OL,13,FDistrict Judge Timothy Boswell
OL,14,Fremanded Hill in custody to appear at
OL,15,FLiverpool Crown Court on 30 April 2024.
OL,17,FThree of her family members were in
OL,18,Fcourt for the hearing, which lasted
OL,19,Ffour minutes.
